org.cef.browser

类 CefMessageRouter.CefMessageRouterConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.browser.CefMessageRouter.CefMessageRouterConfig
  • 封闭类:
    CefMessageRouter

    public static class CefMessageRouter.CefMessageRouterConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to configure the query router. If using multiple router pairs make sure to choose values that do not conflict.
    (用于配置查询路由器。 如果使用多个路由器对，请确保选择不冲突的值)

    • 字段概要

      字段 
      限定符和类型 字段和说明
      java.lang.String jsCancelFunction
      Name of the JavaScript function that will be added to the 'window' object for canceling a pending query. (将添加到“窗口”对象以取消挂起查询的JavaScript函数的名称)
      java.lang.String jsQueryFunction
      Name of the JavaScript function that will be added to the 'window' object for sending a query. (将添加到“窗口”对象以发送查询的JavaScript函数的名称)

    • 字段详细资料

      • jsCancelFunction

        public java.lang.String jsCancelFunction
        Name of the JavaScript function that will be added to the 'window' object for canceling a pending query. The default value is "cefQueryCancel".
        (将添加到“窗口”对象以取消挂起查询的JavaScript函数的名称。 默认值为“cefQueryCancel”)

      • jsQueryFunction

        public java.lang.String jsQueryFunction
        Name of the JavaScript function that will be added to the 'window' object for sending a query. The default value is "cefQuery".
        (将添加到“窗口”对象以发送查询的JavaScript函数的名称。 默认值为“cefQuery”)
